cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM

This paper is about improving the ranking quality of Pinterest image search, which involves information retrieval (IR) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models for ranking, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper involves multimedia content (images), which is relevant to the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
